name: The Granyam Garden Cottage
address: Unnamed Road, Batununggul, Kec. Nusa Penida, Kabupaten Klungkung, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1:
Worst experience 2 cockroaches in the room, manager of the place was super rude, we were staying in their other property before where they had bedbugs cockroaches and they knew and still let people stay here. Don’t go to this place you will probably leave traumatized by their lack of hygiene and rude behavior.

Oh he just threatened me if I don’t get this off he will hunt me down the island and don’t stop to harass me
Or
review 2: We had a wonderful experience staying at Granyam cottage. Beautiful villa in the nature, delicious breakfast and our lovely host Gustu was a perfect combination for best experience. Nice pool and lovely staff. We requested Gustu for local chicken to have local taste, he bought us chicken and his dad made it ready to cook. We cooked and ate together. It was like staying at friend’s home. Had a lots of laugh and fun experience. I would love to come to Nusa penida and stay at granyam cottage again. Cheers to our best host Gastu.
review 3: Best stay i had in my time here in Bali. The location is great when you rent a scooter, because it is right in the center of all the sights. And the best restaurants are 15 min bike ride away. The owner is really helpfull.

name: The Granyam Luxury Bungalow
address: Unnamed Road, 8H66+8GP, Batununggul, Nusa Penida, Klungkung Regency, Bali 80771, Indonesia
review 1: Lovely bungalows and pool set high above the village with views of Mount Agung in Bali. The bungalows are modern,clean, and the bed super comfy. The staff were helpful and the breakfast delicious.
review 2: The place was amazing is truly embodies relaxation! We felt super welcomed, rooms are great! The staff is incredibly friendly and made the time there that much better. would recommend to anyone who wants to be away from the hustle hustle for some peace and quiet!
review 3: Lovely relaxing place far awsy from tourist areas
